Plans for my initiative tracker
Features
	Login Screen
	Server-side backups
	Access said backups on more than one device by getting backup from server

	Viewing players' vigilance and cool skills
	Selecting the number of successes, advantages and triumphs
	Generating slots based on initiative rolled for players and enemies
	Adding or removing enemies from initiative order

	Add Player Form
	View Player
	Edit Player

	Add Enemy/NPC
	View NPC
	Edit NPC

	Start encounter
	View Encounter
	Add Player to Encounter
	Add NPC to Encounter